27:41.572 --> 27:43.400
There's a theme?

27:43.444 --> 27:45.751
[all shout]
- Not okay!

27:45.794 --> 27:47.056
No! Hey!

27:47.100 --> 27:49.102
Not--not okay. Hey!
- Get him.

27:49.145 --> 27:50.930
Summer fun,
summer high jinks.

27:50.973 --> 27:53.584
Listen, you got
to take it down here.

27:53.628 --> 27:54.629
Hey!
- Ha ha ha!

27:54.673 --> 27:56.283
Okay, all right.

27:56.326 --> 27:57.719
Not okay! Oh!

27:57.763 --> 28:00.722
<i>[upbeat rock music]</i>

28:00.766 --> 28:04.639
