28:22.788 --> 28:26.313
Oh, okay, I like it.
Let's see now.

28:26.356 --> 28:29.142
<i>[heartwarming music]</i>

28:29.185 --> 28:35.888
<i>♪</i>

28:41.023 --> 28:44.287
Does the food you eat ever
get caught in your lip metal?

28:44.331 --> 28:46.986
[chuckles]

28:47.029 --> 28:49.858
You're different than before,

28:49.902 --> 28:52.687
like, head-injury different.

28:52.731 --> 28:55.255
You've changed.
- Yes, I know.

28:55.298 --> 28:58.998
You ghosted me
for, like, three years.

28:59.041 --> 29:00.695
I thought you hated me,

29:00.739 --> 29:03.045
Then why did you come here?

29:03.089 --> 29:05.308
To be honest,
I was afraid to.

29:05.352 --> 29:07.354
I mean...

29:07.397 --> 29:09.182
I've changed, too, obviously.

29:09.225 --> 29:12.011
I'm not the little girl
you used to take fishing.

29:13.403 --> 29:14.883
But you're my family.

29:14.927 --> 29:17.451
I was hoping that'd be enough,

29:17.494 --> 29:18.887
'cause if it wasn't enough,

29:18.931 --> 29:23.370
I would have had to go back
to that hellhole camp.

29:23.413 --> 29:25.633
Dial their phone number.

29:29.419 --> 29:32.727
<i>[line trilling]</i>

29:32.771 --> 29:36.122
Hello, my name is
Dr. Harry Vanderspeigle,

29:36.165 --> 29:39.603
and my daughter Liza
isn't going to come back

29:39.647 --> 29:43.085
to your stupid camp.

29:43.129 --> 29:44.739
It is stupid.

29:44.783 --> 29:47.220
You are stupid.
[chuckles]

29:47.263 --> 29:48.874
If you contact her again,

29:48.917 --> 29:50.832
I will find you
and your family.

29:50.876 --> 29:52.747
That should cover it.

29:52.791 --> 29:54.967
Mm-hmm.

29:55.010 --> 29:57.534
[laughs]

29:57.578 --> 29:59.319
Hey...

29:59.362 --> 30:00.842
win me a prize?

30:00.886 --> 30:04.237
<i>[sentimental music]</i>

30:04.280 --> 30:08.850
I will win myself a prize
and consider giving it to you.

30:08.894 --> 30:10.243
Fair enough.

30:10.286 --> 30:16.379
<i>♪</i>

30:16.423 --> 30:19.774
All right, time for
the 52nd Annual Family Day

30:19.818 --> 30:21.384
Hot Chili Pepper
Eating Contest.

30:21.428 --> 30:23.517
[cheers and applause]
