30:23.560 --> 30:25.954
No.
Need to line the stomach.

30:25.998 --> 30:29.001
Trust me, I've won this contest
every year since I was 13,

30:29.044 --> 30:30.872
except the year
that Ethiopian exchange student

30:30.916 --> 30:32.265
threw me for a loop.

30:32.308 --> 30:34.354
Biniyam!
- [laughs] You're so gonna win.

30:34.397 --> 30:36.356
