gets real mad ♪

36:50.686 --> 36:54.255
♪ I don't think he will stay
- What are you thinking?

36:54.299 --> 36:56.126
Terrible, man.

36:57.693 --> 37:01.958
[scattered applause]

37:02.002 --> 37:04.961
<i>[quirky music]</i>

37:05.005 --> 37:07.094
<i>♪</i>

37:11.098 --> 37:14.014
<i>[Samantha Crain's</i> <i>
"We Are The Same"]</i>

37:14.057 --> 37:18.453
<i>♪</i>

37:18.497 --> 37:20.281
- Here, this'll help.
- [groans]

37:20.325 --> 37:23.371
Thanks. I need, like,
six or seven more of these.

37:23.415 --> 37:24.633
[chuckles]

37:24.677 --> 37:26.461
<i>♪ Sole dependency</i>

37:26.505 --> 37:29.334
[sighs]

37:29.377 --> 37:32.641
I shouldn't have said
what I said about you and Jay.

37:32.685 --> 37:34.774
