37:34.817 --> 37:37.124
No, you meant it.

37:37.167 --> 37:39.648
Okay, I meant it.
[both laugh]

37:39.692 --> 37:42.129
I was mad, and I was wrong.
- [sniffles]

37:42.172 --> 37:44.087
No, you weren't.

37:44.131 --> 37:45.654
You were right.

37:45.698 --> 37:47.221
My parents took me
out to dinner,

37:47.265 --> 37:49.397
and my response was
to go get blackout drunk.

37:49.441 --> 37:52.531
Your parents are assholes.

37:52.574 --> 37:55.316
I mean, I love them,
but come on.

37:55.360 --> 37:57.405
I should be better at dealing
with them by now.

37:57.449 --> 37:59.668
I'm not 15.

37:59.712 --> 38:01.496
I'm a mess.

38:01.540 --> 38:03.324
No.

38:03.368 --> 38:05.935
I'm a mess.
Look at me.

38:05.979 --> 38:08.895
I don't want to be messy.
[groans]

38:08.938 --> 38:10.766
I don't want that either.

38:10.810 --> 38:12.594
We can't both be messes
at the same time.

38:12.638 --> 38:14.335
Otherwise it's chaos.

38:14.379 --> 38:16.337
<i>♪</i>

38:16.381 --> 38:20.341
Going to Jimmy's was so dumb.

38:20.385 --> 38:22.996
I just...

38:23.039 --> 38:24.084
[sighs]

38:24.127 --> 38:26.521
He just went through it,
you know?

38:26.565 --> 38:27.609
I mean, he was an asshole,

38:27.653 --> 38:29.785
but he was there
when Jay was born,

38:29.829 --> 38:32.353
and he was there for me
through all the freakouts

38:32.397 --> 38:34.964
after I gave her up.

38:35.008 --> 38:37.706
<i>♪ I would never take</i> <i>
from you... ♪</i>

38:37.750 --> 38:40.753
I guess I'm so used
to being sad with him,

38:40.796 --> 38:42.798
something about it
feels normal.

38:44.409 --> 38:47.977
I don't think
that's supposed to feel normal.

38:48.021 --> 38:50.632
You know, I wasn't around
when all that stuff went down,

38:50.676 --> 38:52.721
but I'm here now.

38:52.765 --> 38:55.594
And I always will be.

38:55.637 --> 38:58.771
You know that, right?

38:58.814 --> 39:01.382
- Right.
- [chuckles]

39:01.426 --> 39:02.775
[sniffles]

39:02.818 --> 39:06.387
When I woke up
on his couch...

39:06.431 --> 39:08.520
I saw that picture of us
from the senior year

39:08.563 --> 39:12.001
where I'm wearing that
stupid football sweatshirt.

39:12.045 --> 39:14.047
[laughs]

39:14.090 --> 39:16.789
That thing is still
in my trunk.

39:18.312 --> 39:20.358
I think you should go
get that sweatshirt.

39:20.401 --> 39:23.404
<i>♪</i>

39:23.448 --> 39:25.711
- Yeah. Yeah.
