39:25.754 --> 39:27.930
- Yeah.
- Why?

39:27.974 --> 39:29.802
[laughs, speaks indistinctly]

39:29.845 --> 39:33.414
- What are you gonna do?
- [speaks indistinctly]

39:33.458 --> 39:37.766
♪

39:37.810 --> 39:39.681
<i>♪ And we</i>

39:39.725 --> 39:42.075
<i>♪</i>

39:42.118 --> 39:45.861
<i>♪ We are the same</i>

39:45.905 --> 39:53.042
<i>♪</i>

39:58.004 --> 40:00.223
We'll only be gone
a couple of days.

40:00.267 --> 40:01.703
You're sure
you're okay here alone?

40:01.747 --> 40:03.052
Ah, of course.

40:03.096 --> 40:05.620
Who cares
if everyone hated the play

40:05.664 --> 40:07.100
and me for writing it?

40:07.143 --> 40:10.146
Not everyone
in the audience hated it.

40:10.190 --> 40:11.757
And that woman
who screamed at you

40:11.800 --> 40:13.062
