complainer moms from school.

40:13.106 --> 40:15.674
♪ Where have
all the daddies gone? ♪

40:15.717 --> 40:18.938
♪ Where did they all go?

40:18.981 --> 40:20.722
You're singing the song.

40:20.766 --> 40:22.985
Yeah,
it's the best song ever.

40:23.029 --> 40:26.641
And the play was awesome.
The blood looked so cool.

40:26.685 --> 40:29.122
See you in a couple days.

40:29.165 --> 40:32.342
♪ Where did Mommy's happy go?

40:32.386 --> 40:35.128
Wow. Did you see that?
Max loved it.

40:35.171 --> 40:38.087
See? You got yourself
all worked up over nothing.

40:38.131 --> 40:40.525
By next year, everyone will
have forgotten all about it,

40:40.568 --> 40:42.004
and you can do another play.

40:42.048 --> 40:44.137
No way.
I mean, you heard Max.

40:44.180 --> 40:45.443
The play worked.

40:45.486 --> 40:48.097
No, we'll--we'll do it
even bigger next year.

40:48.141 --> 40:51.100
You know, bigger boulders,
maybe--maybe even more blood.

40:52.624 --> 40:54.843
Great.

40:54.887 --> 40:56.758
Okay. Bye, honey.
- Okay, bye.

40:56.802 --> 40:59.021
Bye-bye. Okay.

40:59.065 --> 41:02.024
Have fun at your mom's.

41:05.071 --> 41:07.508
- Bye, Dad!
- Bye, honey!

