41:16.952 --> 41:20.086
[indistinct chatter]

41:23.306 --> 41:24.525
Thanks.

41:24.569 --> 41:27.049
Just take care of yourself.

41:27.093 --> 41:28.311
At the end of the day,

41:28.355 --> 41:30.966
you can't depend
on anyone else but you.

41:31.010 --> 41:33.186
My mom would never say
something like that.

41:34.840 --> 41:37.146
But I think you're right.

41:37.190 --> 41:38.887
Thanks.

41:40.715 --> 41:42.064
I--

41:42.108 --> 41:45.590
<i>[emotional music]</i>

41:45.633 --> 41:52.727
<i>♪</i>

41:52.771 --> 41:55.121
You're a better father
than I remember.

41:55.164 --> 41:57.602
I'm glad we got
to spend time together.

41:57.645 --> 42:00.256
I might even miss you a little.

42:00.300 --> 42:02.563
I am glad.

42:02.607 --> 42:04.696
<i>I miss my family, too.</i>

42:04.739 --> 42:06.741
All right, folks.

42:06.785 --> 42:08.700
<i>I have also changed.</i>

42:08.743 --> 42:10.179
Ticket, please.

42:10.223 --> 42:14.401
<i>But the alien in New York</i> <i>
is my family.</i>

42:14.444 --> 42:17.491
<i>So maybe</i> <i>
they will help me anyway.</i>

42:19.667 --> 42:21.277
<i>I have to try.</i>

42:21.321 --> 42:23.584
I am ready to go
to New York now.

42:23.628 --> 42:26.718
<i>♪</i>

42:26.761 --> 42:29.285
<i>I am not worried.</i>

42:29.329 --> 42:32.375
<i>I know I am much more alien</i> <i>
than human.</i>

42:35.727 --> 42:37.859
Sheriff,
can I tell you something?

42:37.903 --> 42:39.818
All right, go ahead.
Lay it on me.

42:39.861 --> 42:42.908
You know
that day the FBI guy came,

42:42.951 --> 42:46.999
the day that neither
of us can remember?

42:47.042 --> 42:49.044
I think an alien
erased our memory.

42:49.088 --> 42:50.785
There, I said it.

42:50.829 --> 42:52.308
Well, I can't speak
for you, Deputy,

42:52.352 --> 42:56.138
but, um, I remember exactly
what I was doing that day.

42:56.182 --> 42:59.402
It was a good day.
Actually, a very good day.

43:01.666 --> 43:03.406
Okay.

43:05.626 --> 43:08.716
<i>[Django Reinhardt's</i> <i>
"La Mer [Beyond the Sea]"]</i>

43:08.760 --> 43:11.632
<i>Only an alien would have</i> <i>
been able to put a memory</i>

43:11.676 --> 43:13.416
<i>in the sheriff's head.</i>

43:13.460 --> 43:17.769
<i>♪</i>

43:17.812 --> 43:20.685
[both laughing]

43:20.728 --> 43:24.863
<i>And if that memory</i> <i>
gave him a good day...</i>

43:24.906 --> 43:27.474
<i>then that is just</i> <i>
a coincidence.</i>

43:27.517 --> 43:34.437
<i>♪</i>
